  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced lamb and cook until browned, about 5 minutes. Stir occasionally to prevent sticking.",
    "Add sliced onions and minced garlic to the pan, cooking for another 3-4 minutes until softened.",
    "Stir in red pepper flakes, paprika, salt, pickled vegetables, and lime juice. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve immediately with steamed basmati rice or naan bread."
